OL,3,CMum glassed man in 'random' attack
OL,4,Coutside pub
OL,6,FA young mother left a man with a
OL,7,F"devastating" injury after using a
OL,8,Fglass in an "unprovoked" attack
OL,9,Foutside a pub.
OL,11,FBlaze Jessop, 21, had been drinking
OL,12,Fwhen she shoved a glass into the man's
OL,13,Fface as a group gathered outside The
OL,14,FGeorge pub in Prince Street,
OL,15,FBridlington.
OL,17,FHull Crown Court heard that the victim
OL,18,Fbled heavily after the incident on 9
OL,19,FApril last year.
