OL,6,FJessop, of Annandale Road, Greatfield
OL,7,Festate, Hull, admitted inflicting
OL,8,Fgrievous bodily harm.
OL,10,FShe had a previous conviction in 2020
OL,11,Ffor assaulting an emergency worker.
OL,13,FMichael Masson, mitigating, said of
OL,14,FJessop: "The defendant accepts that,
OL,15,Fas a result of her actions, a
OL,16,Fdevastating wound was caused to this
OL,17,Fyoung man."
