OL,6,FJudge Tahir Khan KC told Jessop: "You
OL,7,Faccepted that you used a glass, which
OL,8,Fyou smashed against the victim,
OL,9,Fcausing him a significant laceration
OL,10,Fthat ran down the left side of his
OL,11,Fface.
OL,13,F"There was a lot of blood and there is
OL,14,Fsome suggestion of nerve damage as
OL,15,Fwell. The attack upon him by you
OL,16,Fresulted in him feeling the effects of
OL,17,Fthe scar. There is no doubt that this
OL,18,Fwas a serious offence."
