OL,6,FJessop was given a 16-month suspended
OL,7,Fprison sentence, 20 days'
OL,8,Frehabilitation and six months' alcohol
OL,9,Ftreatment.
OL,11,F"If you do breach the order in any
OL,12,Fway, you run the risk of being sent to
OL,13,Fcustody," Judge Khan said.
OL,15,F"If you and I meet again, you will be
OL,16,Fgoing to prison."
